State of North Carolina
v.
Anthony Dove No. 131P01-12 Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 9, 2016 Mr. Anthony Dove, Pro se. Ms. Sherri Lawrence, Assistant Attorney General, Mr. Matthew Delbridge, District Attorney, For State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 14th of December 2015 in this matter for a writ of mandamus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Lenoir County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 9th of June 2016."

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 14th of December 2015 by Defendant to Expedite Petition for Writ of Mandamus:

"Motion Dismissed as moot by order of the Court in conference, this the 9th of June 2016."
